<paragraph blockId="22.[264,1322,657,1443]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[264,416,657,683]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Description.</emphasis>
ɗ. Body about 
<number box="[618,655,657,683]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2.7">2.7</number>
times as long as wide. Rostrum longer than head and pronotum combined, third segment about 
<number box="[756,785,697,723]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="15.0">15</number>
times as long as first, about 
<number box="[1123,1160,697,723]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="3.7">3.7</number>
times as long as second, 
<number box="[397,412,737,763]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="5.0">5</number>
times as long as fourth; second antennal segment about 
<number box="[1102,1117,737,763]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="4.0">4</number>
times as long as first. Pronotum with wide pale markings on lateral sides, 
<number box="[940,954,777,803]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2.0">2</number>
times as wide as long, anterior margin about 
<number box="[427,464,817,843]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="0.6">0.6</number>
times as long as posterior, anterior and posterior margins nearly straight, sides convex; femora stout, over 
<number box="[679,693,857,883]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2.0">2</number>
times as thick as corresponding tibiae, fore coxae round, trochanters triangular; mid tarsus about 
<number box="[832,869,897,923]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="0.5">0.5</number>
times as long as corresponding tibia, hind tarsus nearly 
<number box="[484,521,937,963]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="0.4">0.4</number>
times as long as hind tibia, hind leg distinctly longer than fore and mid legs, tibia nearly 
<number box="[519,555,977,1003]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="1.3">1.3</number>
times as long as femur.
</paragraph>
